百事公司於2003年出售其瓶裝廠<ref name="NYCL p. 7" />，但該公司規定須將標誌牌安置在長島市水岸，並保留該標誌以及附近一塊面積為{{Convert|200|by|60|ft}}的土地之所有權。<ref name="Brill 2017" /><ref name="Walsh 2008">{{cite web|last=Walsh|first=Jeremy|date=2008-08-17|title=Pepsi to bring back landmark LIC sign|url=https://qns.com/story/2008/08/16/pepsi-to-bring-back-landmark-lic-sign/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=QNS.com|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907110858/https://qns.com/story/2008/08/16/pepsi-to-bring-back-landmark-lic-sign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2004年，由於瓶裝廠的拆除工程及龍門廣場州立公園的建設<ref>{{Cite news|last=Dunlap|first=David W.|date=2003-09-24|title=3,200 Apartments to Be Built In Glow of Giant Pepsi Sign|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/24/nyregion/3200-apartments-to-be-built-in-glow-of-giant-pepsi-sign.html|access-date=2020-07-30|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227022553/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/24/nyregion/3200-apartments-to-be-built-in-glow-of-giant-pepsi-sign.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，百事公司將標誌南遷{{Convert|300|ft}}，緊鄰州立公園，並且建造一個臨時基座<ref name="NYCL p. 7" /><ref name="nyt20081210" />，而攝影師{{tsl|en|Vera Lutter|維拉·盧特}}則紀錄了標誌牌拆卸和重組的過程。<ref name="Brill 2017" />隨後該標誌於2008年移回原來的位置，並在同年底再次被拆解，準備重新安裝到長期設置的地點。<ref name="nyt20081210">{{Cite web|last=Dunlap|first=David W.|date=2008-12-10|title=What Happened to the Queens Pepsi Sign|url=https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/12/10/what-happened-to-the-queens-pepsi-sign/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=City Room|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002035058/https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/12/10/what-happened-to-the-queens-pepsi-sign/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Lauinger|first=John|date=2008-11-03|title=Pepsi sign to get lots more pop|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/queens/pepsi-sign-lots-pop-article-1.333696|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907110901/https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/queens/pepsi-sign-lots-pop-article-1.333696|archive-date=2020-09-07|access-date=2020-07-30|website=New York Daily News|language=en}}</ref>2009年初，百事可樂標誌在龍門廣場州立公園的新位置被重新組裝<ref name="Matua 2016">{{cite web|last=Matua|first=Angela|date=2016-04-12|title=Pepsi-Cola sign in Long Island City is officially a New York City landmark|url=https://qns.com/story/2016/04/12/pepsi-cola-sign-in-long-island-city-is-officially-a-new-york-city-landmark/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=QNS.com|language=en|archive-date=2016-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728073412/http://qns.com/story/2016/04/12/pepsi-cola-sign-in-long-island-city-is-officially-a-new-york-city-landmark/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Blumenthal|first=Ralph|date=2009-02-25|title=Letter by Letter, Pepsi Rejoins Skyline|url=https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/02/25/letter-by-letter-pepsi-rejoins-skyline/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=City Room|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003072720/https://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/02/25/letter-by-letter-pepsi-rejoins-skyline/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而百事公司將繼續維護該標誌。<ref name="NYCL p. 8">{{harvnb|Landmarks Preservation Commission|2016|ps=.|p=8}}</ref><ref name="nyt20130710"/>附近的46－10號中心大道（46-10 Center Boulevard）25層公寓開發項目將其8個樓層向內凹陷{{convert|12|ft}}，使公寓的建築外牆位在標誌牌後方{{convert|45|ft}}，該公寓項目位於{{tsl|en|Hunter's Point South|亨特角南}}僅靠州立公園東面的位置。<ref name="nyt20130710">{{Cite news|last=Dunlap|first=David W.|date=2013-07-10|title=Saving a Spot for Pepsi-Cola as a Tower Goes Up|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/11/nyregion/as-a-queens-tower-rises-a-spot-is-saved-for-pepsi-cola.html|access-date=2020-07-29|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321183637/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/11/nyregion/as-a-queens-tower-rises-a-spot-is-saved-for-pepsi-cola.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

