2015年底，紐約市地標保護委員會就是否將百事可樂標誌賦予城市地標的資格再次舉辦公聽會，會上大多數的意見偏向支持，但仍有包括標誌牌擁有者在內的部分人士表示反對<ref name="NYCL p. 1"/>，該標誌也是地標保護委員會積壓十多年但從未成為城市地標的95個景物之一。<ref>{{cite web|last=Matua|first=Angela|date=2016-02-24|title=Pepsi-Cola sign in LIC may become an official landmark by the end of 2016|url=https://qns.com/story/2016/02/24/pepsi-cola-sign-in-lic-will-become-an-official-landmark/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=QNS.com|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701090139/http://qns.com/story/2016/02/24/pepsi-cola-sign-in-lic-will-become-an-official-landmark/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Kimmelman|first=Michael|date=2016-02-17|title=Big Risks as Landmarks Preservation Commission Moves to Prune Proposed Gems|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/18/arts/big-risks-as-landmarks-preservation-commission-moves-to-prune-proposed-gems.html|access-date=2020-07-29|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2018-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105023333/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/18/arts/big-risks-as-landmarks-preservation-commission-moves-to-prune-proposed-gems.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然根據地標保護委員會的規定，城市地標通常需具備30年的歷史，但重建後的標誌牌基本與原版標誌一致，且原版的標誌牌亦早已損毀<ref name="nyt20160412" />，最終百事可樂標誌在2016年4月被正式指定為[[紐約市地標|紐約市地標]]。<ref name="nyt20160412" /><ref name="Matua 2016" />

2019年8月至10月間，百事可樂標誌下方短期安裝了[[捷藍航空|捷藍航空]]的標誌，此舉是由地標保護委員會批准的宣傳活動<ref>{{Cite news|last=Honan|first=Katie|date=2019-08-20|title=JetBlue Tacks Its Name Onto Landmarked Pepsi-Cola Sign in Queens|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/jetblue-tacks-its-name-onto-landmarked-pepsi-cola-sign-in-queens-11566340916|access-date=2020-07-30|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2020-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602111559/https://www.wsj.com/articles/jetblue-tacks-its-name-onto-landmarked-pepsi-cola-sign-in-queens-11566340916|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但其隨後受到當地居民和[[評論家|網路評論員]]的批評<ref name="LIC Post 2019" /><ref>{{cite web|last=Hallum|first=Mark|date=2019-08-21|title='No one wants this': JetBlue logo on Pepsi-Cola sign raises eyebrows in Long Island City|url=https://qns.com/story/2019/08/21/no-one-wants-this-jetblue-logo-on-pepsi-cola-sign-raises-eyebrows-in-long-island-city/|access-date=2020-07-30|website=QNS.com|language=en|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914050431/https://qns.com/story/2019/08/21/no-one-wants-this-jetblue-logo-on-pepsi-cola-sign-raises-eyebrows-in-long-island-city/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，百事公司營銷副總裁南西·魯尼（Nancy Rooney）則表示，臨時增加的標誌牌是慶祝百事可樂與捷藍航空建立合作關係的「完美象徵」。<ref>{{cite web|date=2019-08-21|title=JetBlue addition to Pepsi sign leaves bad taste for some|url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/jetblue-addition-pepsi-sign-leaves-bad-taste-65103362|access-date=2020-07-30|website=ABC News|publisher=Associated Press|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907110900/https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/jetblue-addition-pepsi-sign-leaves-bad-taste-65103362|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=百事可樂與捷藍合作 廣告牌混搭民眾抗議|url=https://www.worldjournal.com/6462407/article-百事可樂與捷藍合作-廣告牌混搭民眾抗議/|author=馬永慶|date=2019-08-21|accessdate=2020-09-07|work=[[世界日報_(北美)|世界日報]]|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907110920/https://www.worldjournal.com/6462407/article-%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E8%88%87%E6%8D%B7%E8%97%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%89%8C%E6%B7%B7%E6%90%AD%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

